<p><em>"Really excited about this evening. Many Zoom calls and a trip to Amsterdam later, I'm excited to share &ndash; and to wear &ndash; what we have been up to."</em></p>
<p>Explaining that the design was crafted from 800 recycled water bottles and organic silk, she added:&nbsp;<em>"One year in the making. Yep &ndash; we are happy. But my favorite? The fries after the red carpet."</em></p>
<p>As she made her way to the event in the luxury car, Sharapova confessed: <em>"I may look cosy but I'm just hoping this seat position doesn't ruin any of the hand-stitched petals."</em></p>
