            <title>French say ‘non merci’ to nonbinary pronouns</title>
            <link>https://www.rt.com/op-ed/541774-france-importing-wokisme-gender-fail/</link>
            <guid>61a641c085f54004124be0ee</guid>
            <pubDate>2021-12-01T08:12:36+00:00</pubDate>
            <author>RT</author>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[
                <!doctype html>
<html lang="en" prefix="op: http://media.facebook.com/op#">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
